title: elf Studio High Definition Loose Face Powder
description: The e.l.f. High Definition Powder is a translucent, versatile loose powder that creates a flawless, "soft focus" effect to the skin. Masks fine lines and imperfections for a glowing, radiant complexion. This incredibly soft and invisible powder is ideal for everyday wear, either alone or over your favorite e.l.f. foundation. Our HD Powder is a makeup artist and e.l.f. customer favorite.

title: Sexy Hair Big Volume Shampoo and Conditioner Duo Set 33.8oz
description: The Sexy Hair Big Sexy Hair Volume Shampoo & Conditioner is perfect to use on thin, normal to dry hair and combination hair types for thicker looking, shiny hair. Formulated to protect the color of your hair, it has deep conditioning agents which moisturize hair deeply, leaving it soft, supple and lustrous. The Sexy Hair Big Sexy Hair Volume contains natural extracts like wheat proteins, Panthenol and other extracts that clean, moisturize and add the right amount of fluffiness to your hair.

title: Too Faced Better Than Sex Mascara 0.17 ounce - Mini Travel size
description: Inspired by the curves of a woman's body, the hourglass-shaped brush was designed with extra stiff bristles to maximize the performance of this carbon black, collagen-fueled formula. One coat and lashes are full and defined. Two coats and lashes are even more luscious, curled, and dramatic. Three coats help you achieve the most intense, black, multidimensional lashes possible.
